'''Alexander Olof Bernhardsson''' (born 8 September 1998) is a Swedish professional footballer who plays as a [[forward (association football)|forward]] for {{German football updater|Kiel}} club [[Holstein Kiel]] and the [[Sweden men's national football team|Sweden national team]].<ref name="SW">{{Soccerway|alexander-bernhardsson/555065|access-date=26 August 2021}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://fotbolltransfers.com/site/player/9309|title=12. Alexander Bernhardsson|publisher=Fotbolltransfers|language=Swedish|access-date=26 August 2021}}</ref>

==Club career==
On 22 January 2024, Bernhardsson signed a contract with [[2. Bundesliga]] club [[Holstein Kiel]] until 30 June 2027.<ref>{{cite web|publisher=Holstein Kiel|url=https://www.holstein-kiel.de/news-herren/schwede-alexander-bernhardsson-verstaerkt-kieler-offensive/|title=SCHWEDE ALEXANDER BERNHARDSSON VERSTÄRKT KIELER OFFENSIVE|trans-title=SWEDE ALEXANDER BERNHARDSSON STRENGTHENS KIEL'S OFFENSE|date=22 January 2024|access-date=22 January 2024|language=de|archive-date=23 January 2024|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20240123075836/https://www.holstein-kiel.de/news-herren/schwede-alexander-bernhardsson-verstaerkt-kieler-offensive/|url-status=dead}}</ref>

==International career ==
Bernhardsson made his full international debut for [[Sweden men's national football team|Sweden]] on 9 January 2023, playing for 90 minutes in a [[Exhibition game|friendly]] 2–0 win against [[Finland national football team|Finland]].<ref>{{Cite web |title=Sverige - Finland - Matchfakta - Svensk fotboll |url=https://www.svenskfotboll.se/matchfakta/sverige-finland-landskamper-herr-senior/5386999/ |access-date=10 January 2023 |website=www.svenskfotboll.se |language=sv}}</ref>

On 12 May 2026, Bernhardsson was named in the Sweden squad for the [[2026 FIFA World Cup]].<ref>{{Cite web |date=2026-05-12 |title=Mystiskt inlägg efter petningen |url=https://www.expressen.se/sport/fotboll/landslaget/har-ar-sveriges-trupp-till-fotbolls-vm-2026/ |access-date=2026-05-15 |website=www.expressen.se |language=sv}}</ref>

